    <p>
        This <a target="_blank" href="https://www.syncfusion.com/aspnet-mvc-ui-controls/charts/chart-types/spline-area-chart" aria-label="ASP.NET MVC Spline Area Chart">ASP.NET MVC Spline Area Chart<span class="sr-only">opens in a new tab</span></a> example visualizes inflation rate comparison for two countries by using spline area series.
    </p>
